column8:
so i just moved here from texas and im getting my ba in art
history. i have a part time job as a receptionist at an
environmental non-profit. i'm pretty busy with studying and work,
but i'm always happy to chat :)
column9:
i'm getting my ba in art history(focusing on art in culture),
working to support the environment (by answering phone calls),
starting a new art project (im making puzzle boxes),
enjoying this new part of the country (omg the weather).

turning in essays late, overusing the comma, exploring the great
outdoors, thinking strangely.
